{"title":"Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4″ adds wider option to their lightest, fastest, race-ready MTB tire","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/25/pirelli-scorpion-xc-rc-2-4-adds-wider-option-to-their-lightest-fastest-race-ready-mtb-tire/","date":1624644035000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Pirelli keeps filling out their more refined and ever-growing <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/05/29/pirelli-expands-scorpion-mountain-bike-tire-line-reshaped-into-xc-trail-enduro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mountain bike tire line-up</a>, now adding a wider 2.4″ version of the Scorpion XC RC cross-country race tire. It’s a subtle update for their fastest-rolling MTB tire. But with larger volume and both extra-light or reinforced casing options, it’ll go a long way towards expanding the real application of this fast, small-knobbed XC tire from beyond race day to riding dry, hardpack trails as well.</p><h2>Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4″ wider cross-country tire opens up to dry trails</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall.jpg\" alt=\"Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4&quot; light wide mountain bike cross-country race tire yellow label only\" width=\"1200\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall-696x418.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall-1068x641.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135123/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-sidewall-700x420.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\"></a></p><p>While we’re probably still most anxious to learn more about their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/04/14/pirelli-scorpion-gravity-teases-ews-dh-race-tires-developed-with-mtb-legend-fabien-barel/\">all-new upcoming gravity tires</a> developed under Fabien Barel, Pirelli has slipped out a wider 2.4″ XC tire that’s maybe more useful to a great number of riders. Keeping the same tread pattern as the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/05/26/pirelli-scorpion-xc-rc-mountain-bike-tire-delivers-race-ready-speed-grip-light-weight/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">original 2.2″ XC RC</a> that debuted just over a year ago, only scaled up to be 10% wider, it’s still meant for going fast over the same generally hardpacked terrain – with low &amp; continuous fast-rolling center blocks that transition to wider, open should lugs for cornering grip.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread.jpg\" alt=\"Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4&quot; light wide mountain bike cross-country race tire tread\" width=\"1200\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread-696x418.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread-1068x641.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135129/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-tread-700x420.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\"></a></p><p>But as even more than the original that was designed for the varied surface of the XCO World Cup race circuit with Trek-Pirelli MTB team racers, this substantially larger volume lets riders run significantly lower pressure to find grip over the occasional wet rock &amp; root.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass.jpg\" alt=\"Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4&quot; light wide mountain bike cross-country race tire mud &amp; grass\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass-696x464.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135109/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-mud-and-grass-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\"></a></p><p>This is still generally a dry conditions tire, not really intended for much mud which can clog its lugs. But now optimized for the light 30mm internal rims that are popping up even under XC pros, it likely becomes a more versatile tire overall – especially for more hardpack singletrack riding in its reinforced sidewall version.</p><h3>Tech Details</h3><figure id=\"attachment_237116\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-237116\"><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings.jpg\" alt=\"2020 Pirelli Scorpion XC, Trail &amp; Enduro MTB mountain bike tire range&nbsp;\" width=\"1600\" height=\"650\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-297x121.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-800x325.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-120x49.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-768x312.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-1536x624.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-696x283.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-1068x434.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-1034x420.jpg 1034w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-297x121.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-800x325.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-120x49.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-768x312.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-1536x624.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-696x283.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-1068x434.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/2020-Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-cross-country-mountain-bike-tires_LITE-lightweight-supple-and-ProWall-reinforced-120tpi-casings-1034x420.jpg 1034w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-237116\">Lite (left) or ProWall reinforced (right)</figcaption></figure><p>Construction is exactly the same as the original XC RC, with supple 120tpi casing and Pirelli’s single compound SmartGrip rubber. Much like the rest of the lightweight XC range, two sidewall options are offered with the same light casing. Lite omits any extra reinforcement to maximize speed &amp; suppleness. And ProWall adds an extra layer of woven nylon reinforcement at the sidewalls to protect against cuts and also offer more sidewall support at lower pressures.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete.jpg\" alt=\"Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4&quot; light wide mountain bike cross-country race tire complete\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-297x223.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-800x600.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-120x90.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-696x522.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-1068x801.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-560x420.jpg 560w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-80x60.jpg 80w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135102/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-complete-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\"></a></p><p>One new feature that seems to be mostly aesthetic (and that also popped up on the latest <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/16/pirelli-p7-sport-clincher-training-tire-is-grippy-durable-and-way-more-affordable/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">P7 road tire</a>), the new 2.4″ Scorpion XC RC gets Pirelli’s signature sidewall patterning, much like you see on their motorsports tires.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight.jpg\" alt=\"Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4&quot; light wide mountain bike cross-country race tire, 695g actual weight\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-696x392.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-1068x601.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135054/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-695g-actual-weight-747x420.jpg 747w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\"></a></p><p>The 29er-only 2.4″ tire is said to add 50g over the 2.2″ version with claimed weights of 650g in Lite casing or 700g in ProWall casing. The ProWall test samples we got ahold of weighed even a bit under that at 691 &amp; 699g, respectively (<em>695g average</em>).</p><h3>Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4″ – Pricing &amp; availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side.jpg\" alt=\"Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4&quot; light wide mountain bike cross-country race tire sidewall\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side-696x464.jpg 696w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/25135115/Pirelli-Scorpion-XC-RC-light-wide-mountain-bike-cross-country-race-tire_2-4-inch-side-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\"></a></p><p>Available only in team yellow sidewall labels, the wider Pirelli Scorpion XC RC 2.4″ tires have officially appeared on Pirelli’s website, but are still trickling our to various retailers. We don’t have official pricing from Pirelli other than that they should be around the cost of the 2.2″ version ($70 / 60€). But we have seen a couple shops already offering them, selling for the same price.</p><p><a href=\"https://velo.pirelli.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>velo.Pirelli.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"92971ee47b4d3c4b298b2dbca0eca1db7291ed396a23f18be452137dab93bd86","category":"Cycling"}